OL,3,CHeatwave possible across Southern
OL,4,CEngland as 'warm plume' moves towards
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FThere's a chance that parts of
OL,8,FSouthern England could be in heatwave
OL,9,Fconditions by the end of this week,
OL,10,Falthough thunderstorms and rain
OL,11,Fshowers are also likely, forecasters
OL,12,Fhave said.
OL,14,FThe Met Office said the south and
OL,15,Fsouth east of England are likely to
OL,16,Fsee temperatures rise to 28C or higher
OL,17,Fby Thursday.
OL,19,FSunday brought sunshine and light
OL,20,Fwinds, with the highest temperatures
OL,21,Fseen in the South West.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
