OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781524080
OL,3,CHeatwave possible across Southern
OL,4,CEngland as 'warm plume' moves towards
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,F"Other areas will warm up, but it's
OL,8,Falso very humid so they are likely to
OL,9,Fbe cloudy, with rain and showers.
OL,11,F"By Thursday we're looking at around
OL,12,F28C in London, so certainly pushing
OL,13,Finto the high 20s."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@SO]
